function Start()
	--Create Lyndon clone and override anim set
		idLyndonClone = Hydra.CreatePersonalClone(actor_Lyndon)
		idQuestOwner = Hydra.QuestGetOwner()
		
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idLyndonClone) then	
	--Hydra.QActorWait(idLyndonClone, 1)
		
	--Orton voices disapproval
		Hydra.QActorPlayConversation(conv_Lyndon_01d, idQuestOwner, idLyndonClone)
		
	--Play transition animation
		Hydra.QActorClearAnimSetOverride(idLyndonClone)
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idLyndonClone, loc_LyndonWalkTo, "NPC_WALK", true)
		Hydra.QActorDeletePersonalClone(idLyndonClone, 1.5)
	end

	Hydra.Wait(3.0)
	Hydra.EventSendToActor("LyndonDagger", idSelf, idSelf)

end

function Start(idActor, snoQuest)
	--Lyndon Behavior
	idLyndonFollower = Hydra.QuestGetFollower("NPC_QST_Lyndon_Follower")
	idQuestOwner = Hydra.QuestGetOwner()
	
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idLyndonFollower) then
		Hydra.QuestFollowerTakeOwnership(idLyndonFollower)
		Hydra.QActorPlayConversation(conv_Lyndon_04e, idQuestOwner, idLyndonFollower)
		
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idLyndonFollower, actor_LyndonPostAmbush, "NPC_Walk_Fast", true)
		Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(idLyndonFollower, actor_LyndonPostAmbush)
		Hydra.QActorWaitForConversationFinished(idLyndonFollower, conv_Lyndon_04e)
		
		Hydra.QActorDelete(idLyndonFollower)
	end
end
